{
  "texts": [
    "They keep track of the files when they change, how they change, and who changed them by logging all the information.",
    "These logs are sent through agents that are deployed in the end-host systems.",
    "To enable FIM, we make the required changes in the configuration file of the SIEM agent.",
    "Syscheck is enabled to monitor the system checks in real time.",
    "The directories that need to be monitored are specified."
  ]
}